flowchart TD
    A[Load Dataset] --> B[Preprocess Images]
    B --> C[Split Data: Train/Val/Test]
    C --> D[Data Augmentation]
    D --> E[Load Pre-trained VGG16]
    E --> F[Build Classification Model]
    F --> G[Train Phase 1: Frozen Base]
    G --> H[Train Phase 2: Fine-tuning]
    H --> I[Evaluate Model]
    I --> J[Generate Metrics & Visualizations]
    J --> K[Save Model]
    K --> L[Deploy UI]
    L --> M[User Image Upload]
    M --> N[Prediction]
    
    style E fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style G fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style H fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style N fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
